---
title: Pistachio Pangrattato Chicken with Green Bean Salad and Mustard Vinaigrette
description: Toasted bread crumbs , pistachios and a drizzle of oil get tossed together to make a crunchie pangrattato. Blistered beans, and onions are tossed with spring mix and a simple vinaigrette for a crisp summer salad!
